1)  insert the flash drive
2)  open notepad
3) type the following code
  [autorun]
  icon=m.ico          #m is the name of image(it should have .ico as its extension)
  label="hi"          #the name that i want to give to my flash drive or pen drive
4)  save the file with name autorun.inf in pendrive's root directory (don't save it into a folder in pendrive)
5)  also save the image in pendrive's root directory
6) now remove the pendrive and reinsert again and enjoy!!
  
